1
00:00:07,825 --> 00:00:09,065
‎SAY NO TO PIRACY, SUPPORT ORIGINALS

2
00:01:39,185 --> 00:01:41,785
‎ADAPTED FROM XI XING’S NOVEL
‎QUEEN CHU‎ ON QIDIAN.COM

3
00:01:46,145 --> 00:01:49,625
The Emperor passed away!

4
00:01:49,705 --> 00:01:52,785
The Anping Rebellion came to an end.

5
00:01:52,865 --> 00:01:57,145
In this life,
I cut off Xiao Xun's path to the throne.

6
00:01:57,225 --> 00:02:02,105
But this game to crush him has just begun.

7
00:02:02,625 --> 00:02:05,385
Your Highness, congratulations
on getting what you want.

8
00:02:06,505 --> 00:02:07,745
The same to you, Grand Mentor Deng.

9
00:02:07,825 --> 00:02:08,665
DENG YI, THE GRAND MENTOR

10
00:02:08,744 --> 00:02:10,905
You got wealth and honor
as you had longed for.

11
00:02:12,625 --> 00:02:14,305
The Imperial Guard Commander was involved

12
00:02:14,385 --> 00:02:16,065
and executed.

13
00:02:17,265 --> 00:02:18,305
This position

14
00:02:18,865 --> 00:02:21,305
concerns the entire imperial city
and even the royal clan.

15
00:02:22,345 --> 00:02:23,465
Your Highness.

16
00:02:24,865 --> 00:02:25,745
Anyone in mind?

17
00:02:34,025 --> 00:02:34,865
Jiu.

18
00:02:56,025 --> 00:02:57,025
Your Highness,

19
00:02:58,425 --> 00:02:59,385
what do you mean?

20
00:03:00,865 --> 00:03:02,505
This is my first order.

21
00:03:03,385 --> 00:03:04,745
Fu Jiu, retainer of the Chu Clan,

22
00:03:04,825 --> 00:03:06,305
will be promoted
to the Imperial Guard Commander.

23
00:03:07,105 --> 00:03:08,905
He can be armed at court.

24
00:03:10,145 --> 00:03:11,545
Any objection, Grand Mentor?

25
00:03:27,385 --> 00:03:28,705
IMPERIAL GUARD

26
00:03:31,265 --> 00:03:32,505
Don't regret it.

27
00:03:33,425 --> 00:03:35,345
Don't make me regret it.

28
00:03:56,225 --> 00:03:59,185
General! Urgent message from the Capital!

29
00:03:59,265 --> 00:04:01,345
Urgent message from the Capital!

30
00:04:01,945 --> 00:04:02,865
General!

31
00:04:06,345 --> 00:04:08,145
General, message from the Capital!

32
00:04:12,905 --> 00:04:13,865
THE EMPEROR IS DEAD.
HIS FINAL EDICT NAMES CHU ZHAO AS

33
00:04:13,945 --> 00:04:14,985
GRAND PRINCESS,
TO CO-RULE WITH THE GRAND MENTOR

34
00:04:24,545 --> 00:04:27,065
His Majesty has died. Zhao…

35
00:04:28,345 --> 00:04:29,425
She's the Grand Princess now.

36
00:04:30,945 --> 00:04:33,505
What on earth has she gone through?

37
00:04:33,585 --> 00:04:35,865
Complicated infighting in the court

38
00:04:36,465 --> 00:04:39,785
is far more fierce
than that on the frontier.

39
00:04:39,865 --> 00:04:41,985
At least, she's safe now.

40
00:04:43,705 --> 00:04:45,225
Glad she's safe.

41
00:04:47,625 --> 00:04:49,545
General, enemies are invading!

42
00:04:51,705 --> 00:04:53,665
Arm up! Move out!

43
00:05:11,265 --> 00:05:13,145
TAIJI HALL

44
00:05:17,705 --> 00:05:20,345
His Majesty has arrived.

45
00:05:42,585 --> 00:05:43,585
Zhao.

46
00:05:46,345 --> 00:05:47,225
I want Zhao to be here.

47
00:05:47,305 --> 00:05:48,705
XIAO XUN, HEIR TO THE LORD OF XIAONAN

48
00:05:48,785 --> 00:05:49,985
XIE YANFANG, THE PRIME MINISTER

49
00:05:50,065 --> 00:05:51,265
DENG YI, THE GRAND MENTOR

50
00:05:51,345 --> 00:05:52,345
Your Majesty,

51
00:05:52,865 --> 00:05:54,585
this is inappropriate.

52
00:05:56,225 --> 00:05:58,225
Yeah, Your Majesty.

53
00:05:58,305 --> 00:06:00,305
There is no precedent.

54
00:06:00,905 --> 00:06:02,065
Let the Grand Princess enter.

55
00:06:20,665 --> 00:06:22,025
Yu, what's wrong?

56
00:06:22,105 --> 00:06:24,265
Zhao, I don't want to walk alone.

57
00:06:24,345 --> 00:06:25,745
You walk with me, all right?

58
00:06:26,465 --> 00:06:29,705
If a woman interferes with politics,
the state will collapse.

59
00:06:29,785 --> 00:06:31,465
Please behave, Your Highness.

60
00:06:34,225 --> 00:06:38,225
Chamberlain, don't you remember
what happened before?

61
00:06:38,305 --> 00:06:41,705
When Dowager Empress Xie
ruled behind the curtain,

62
00:06:41,785 --> 00:06:44,105
you were the first to urge
the emperor to take the throne.

63
00:06:45,305 --> 00:06:48,145
Your Majesty, time to move on.

64
00:07:00,625 --> 00:07:03,345
DILIGENT AND VIRTUOUS

65
00:07:57,145 --> 00:07:59,105
Kneel.

66
00:08:00,865 --> 00:08:05,305
Your Majesty, may you have longevity

67
00:08:05,385 --> 00:08:07,985
and a prosperous reign!

68
00:08:10,385 --> 00:08:11,625
Rise.

69
00:08:12,505 --> 00:08:14,785
Thank you, Your Majesty.

70
00:08:39,345 --> 00:08:41,625
Mr. Xie, still here?

71
00:08:42,784 --> 00:08:43,985
I've lingered for a moment

72
00:08:44,625 --> 00:08:48,265
to thank you on His Majesty's behalf.

73
00:08:50,585 --> 00:08:51,825
It's so polite of you, Mr. Xie.

74
00:08:51,905 --> 00:08:54,185
I don't know how I should reply.

75
00:08:55,265 --> 00:08:57,585
You're from the direct line
of the Xie Clan of Gaoyang.

76
00:08:57,665 --> 00:09:00,025
And by blood, you're Yu's uncle.

77
00:09:00,545 --> 00:09:04,065
You can call him
by his nickname in private.

78
00:09:06,705 --> 00:09:08,465
Then let me thank you, Your Highness,

79
00:09:09,345 --> 00:09:12,625
on behalf of my clan, for saving Yu's life

80
00:09:12,705 --> 00:09:14,185
and keeping his throne.

81
00:09:14,945 --> 00:09:16,425
You flatter me, Mr. Xie.

82
00:09:16,505 --> 00:09:19,665
Yu and I will rely on you and your clan.

83
00:09:19,745 --> 00:09:21,585
You're modest, Your Highness.

84
00:09:21,665 --> 00:09:23,465
I know it perfectly well.

85
00:09:23,545 --> 00:09:26,425
You didn't get where you are
by relying on my clan.

86
00:09:27,025 --> 00:09:29,505
Instead, my clan relied on you.

87
00:09:30,425 --> 00:09:31,945
Otherwise,

88
00:09:32,025 --> 00:09:35,865
I wouldn't have had a position
in the court.

89
00:09:37,105 --> 00:09:40,305
Since we're in the same boat,
forget about the formalities.

90
00:09:40,905 --> 00:09:46,185
When we're outside the court,
I'll call you Yanfang. All right?

91
00:09:49,385 --> 00:09:50,665
It's my honor.

92
00:09:51,425 --> 00:09:52,825
After you come back here,

93
00:09:52,905 --> 00:09:54,745
you look very well.

94
00:09:55,585 --> 00:09:58,665
I wonder what illness

95
00:09:58,745 --> 00:10:01,425
made you leave the Capital
for a long recovery.

96
00:10:05,385 --> 00:10:06,985
A long-standing illness.

97
00:10:07,585 --> 00:10:09,025
Thank you for your concern.

98
00:10:09,785 --> 00:10:12,945
In the previous life,
he was best at disguising.

99
00:10:13,025 --> 00:10:16,625
His clan had a century-long history
with profound impact.

100
00:10:16,705 --> 00:10:18,385
To put Xiao Xun off his guard,

101
00:10:18,465 --> 00:10:19,985
he feigned illness and stayed in Gaoyang.

102
00:10:20,585 --> 00:10:24,265
But he secretly gathered private troops
and expanded his power.

103
00:10:24,345 --> 00:10:28,145
A man like him, who keeps a low profile,

104
00:10:28,225 --> 00:10:30,385
is more likely to have the last laugh.

105
00:10:35,025 --> 00:10:36,825
Why do you stare at me like that?

106
00:10:37,905 --> 00:10:39,465
Am I untidily dressed?

107
00:10:41,585 --> 00:10:43,825
I was just thinking…

108
00:10:44,745 --> 00:10:48,785
Yanfang, you're an extraordinary
young man.

109
00:10:48,865 --> 00:10:49,945
Among all the ministers,

110
00:10:50,025 --> 00:10:54,545
I've never seen anyone who could be
even half as smart as you.

111
00:10:56,865 --> 00:10:58,865
I wonder how sincere you are

112
00:11:00,185 --> 00:11:01,465
when you praise me.

113
00:11:02,265 --> 00:11:04,185
Every word I say is sincere.

114
00:11:04,905 --> 00:11:06,865
You're a master strategist.

115
00:11:06,945 --> 00:11:11,585
I'm waiting for you to advise me
on what the Lord of Xiaonan will do next.

116
00:11:13,585 --> 00:11:17,545
The Lord of Xiaonan
didn't mourn the late Emperor

117
00:11:17,625 --> 00:11:20,065
or pay homage to the new emperor.

118
00:11:20,665 --> 00:11:23,345
His ambition is all too evident.

119
00:11:24,345 --> 00:11:28,145
The Grand Mentor has sent nearby troops
to Xiaonan Prefecture secretly

120
00:11:28,225 --> 00:11:30,745
in the name of hunting
remnants of the rebels.

121
00:11:31,425 --> 00:11:33,865
The Lord of Xiaonan
has schemed for over two decades.

122
00:11:34,465 --> 00:11:37,665
I'm afraid a lot of things
are no longer under the court's control.

123
00:11:38,745 --> 00:11:40,545
Can't we strike first?

124
00:11:42,185 --> 00:11:43,585
Not until we have a just reason.

125
00:11:44,465 --> 00:11:48,065
The Lord of Xiaonan declared
he was overwhelmed with grief

126
00:11:48,145 --> 00:11:50,145
and bedridden
over the late Emperor's death.

127
00:11:50,785 --> 00:11:52,465
So, he couldn't come here.

128
00:11:54,065 --> 00:11:55,985
And Yu is his junior.

129
00:11:56,065 --> 00:11:57,225
We must placate him.

130
00:11:57,305 --> 00:11:58,825
What's worse,

131
00:11:58,905 --> 00:12:01,105
foes from the Northern Desert
are lurking on the frontier.

132
00:12:02,585 --> 00:12:04,745
New court, young emperor.
Internal and external troubles.

133
00:12:05,865 --> 00:12:07,985
Our state is too fragile
to survive unrest.

134
00:12:08,905 --> 00:12:10,465
That's why the late Emperor's edict stated

135
00:12:10,545 --> 00:12:12,545
Xiao Xun made contributions
in saving the throne.

136
00:12:13,505 --> 00:12:16,305
Otherwise, his father
might have an excuse for rebellion.

137
00:12:17,105 --> 00:12:19,585
But actually, Xiao Xun
is the mastermind behind this.

138
00:12:20,665 --> 00:12:23,385
He set up the trap to kill
the Crown Prince and Princess.

139
00:12:24,225 --> 00:12:26,225
The Crown Princess is my eldest sister.

140
00:12:27,385 --> 00:12:28,985
She's like my mother.

141
00:12:29,785 --> 00:12:34,265
I'm the mortal enemy
of Xiao Xun and his father.

142
00:12:35,145 --> 00:12:37,545
One day, I'll kill them with my own hands

143
00:12:38,985 --> 00:12:40,425
to avenge my sister.

144
00:12:41,745 --> 00:12:43,425
But not now.

145
00:12:44,025 --> 00:12:46,705
Xiao Xun appears to be the imperial uncle.

146
00:12:46,785 --> 00:12:48,665
But actually, he's still a hostage.

147
00:12:49,345 --> 00:12:52,705
Don't worry, Your Highness.
Take everything slowly.

148
00:12:53,425 --> 00:12:55,225
Do not rush things.

149
00:13:01,945 --> 00:13:02,985
I understand.

150
00:13:04,065 --> 00:13:06,025
Thank you for your instructions.

151
00:13:06,905 --> 00:13:10,305
If you have any further confusion,
summon me anytime.

152
00:13:20,705 --> 00:13:21,785
Be careful.

153
00:13:24,025 --> 00:13:25,305
The paths in this palace

154
00:13:27,185 --> 00:13:28,025
are treacherous.

155
00:13:44,305 --> 00:13:47,265
So, someone like Xie Yanfang,
upright and noble,

156
00:13:47,345 --> 00:13:49,945
also wants to kill people out of hatred.

157
00:13:51,665 --> 00:13:54,105
Since you also intend to oppose Xiao Xun,

158
00:13:54,185 --> 00:13:56,705
then don't blame me
for taking advantage of you.

159
00:14:03,305 --> 00:14:07,385
The Xie Clan of Gaoyang
came to rescue with 5,000 private troops.

160
00:14:07,465 --> 00:14:08,305
It's him.

161
00:14:09,545 --> 00:14:10,465
The Xie Clan.

162
00:14:10,545 --> 00:14:14,185
We heard your mother worked in a brothel.

163
00:14:14,265 --> 00:14:16,385
Our clan doesn't want dirty people.

164
00:14:16,465 --> 00:14:19,665
Since you're just like your mother,

165
00:14:20,265 --> 00:14:22,185
how about we pierce your ear

166
00:14:22,265 --> 00:14:23,705
and dress you up?

167
00:14:23,785 --> 00:14:25,785
Maybe you'll fetch a good price.

168
00:14:25,865 --> 00:14:27,385
You can endure a lot. One more.

169
00:14:28,825 --> 00:14:29,945
Stop.

170
00:14:30,545 --> 00:14:32,985
Uncle, it's really kind of you.

171
00:14:33,065 --> 00:14:35,305
You even pity an illegitimate child.

172
00:14:35,385 --> 00:14:38,745
Xie Xiao, you and your peers
bullied the weak boy.

173
00:14:38,825 --> 00:14:40,505
Do you know how you should be punished?

174
00:14:40,585 --> 00:14:43,505
Do you want me
to take you to the ancestral hall

175
00:14:43,585 --> 00:14:44,705
and make you kneel?

176
00:14:45,345 --> 00:14:47,465
Uncle, we're wrong. We'll leave now.

177
00:14:53,505 --> 00:14:55,585
It hurts, huh? Go get some medicine.

178
00:14:57,185 --> 00:14:58,225
No need.

179
00:14:59,385 --> 00:15:01,145
Your ear…

180
00:15:01,225 --> 00:15:03,105
Why do you wear that?

181
00:15:03,185 --> 00:15:06,425
-If people see it…
-I'm not afraid of being seen.

182
00:15:06,505 --> 00:15:09,665
This will become
part of my flesh and blood

183
00:15:10,305 --> 00:15:13,105
and remind me day after day not to forget

184
00:15:13,945 --> 00:15:14,865
how they pierced

185
00:15:15,465 --> 00:15:16,785
my ear.

186
00:15:16,865 --> 00:15:22,145
And one day, they will be pierced by me.

187
00:15:23,065 --> 00:15:25,185
How dare you rebel?

188
00:15:25,265 --> 00:15:26,865
Your whole clan may be executed!

189
00:15:29,185 --> 00:15:30,945
That's just what I want.

190
00:15:31,905 --> 00:15:33,065
Congrats, Yanlai.

191
00:15:35,505 --> 00:15:37,625
With the Commander's token,

192
00:15:38,745 --> 00:15:39,785
you look impressive.

193
00:15:41,905 --> 00:15:43,625
The Grand Princess

194
00:15:44,785 --> 00:15:47,145
isn't as weak as you think she is.

195
00:15:47,745 --> 00:15:49,065
She's indeed extraordinary.

196
00:15:50,985 --> 00:15:53,785
You worked for Chu Ling for so many years.

197
00:15:54,425 --> 00:15:58,185
You know more about Miss Chu than I do.

198
00:15:59,065 --> 00:16:01,185
She acted perfectly.

199
00:16:02,625 --> 00:16:05,825
But sadly, she's way too impatient.

200
00:16:07,145 --> 00:16:08,585
I'm quite curious.

201
00:16:09,185 --> 00:16:11,425
Why did she suddenly hate Xiao Xun?

202
00:16:12,145 --> 00:16:15,265
How did this engaged couple
become estranged?

203
00:16:16,145 --> 00:16:17,985
Why can't they get along?

204
00:16:19,025 --> 00:16:20,625
From the very beginning,

205
00:16:22,025 --> 00:16:23,985
Xiao Xun wasn't after Chu Zhao,

206
00:16:25,105 --> 00:16:27,225
but the frontier troops
under Chu Ling's control.

207
00:16:27,905 --> 00:16:30,785
She would notice it if she weren't a fool.

208
00:16:34,745 --> 00:16:36,265
It sounds like…

209
00:16:38,105 --> 00:16:39,945
Yanlai, you think she's clever.

210
00:16:41,705 --> 00:16:45,985
I've never heard you
praise anyone else like that.

211
00:16:50,585 --> 00:16:52,265
The way you look at her…

212
00:16:54,545 --> 00:16:57,065
It's like how you look at your pet.

213
00:16:58,585 --> 00:16:59,585
However,

214
00:17:00,185 --> 00:17:02,345
she's a wolf growing up in the desert.

215
00:17:03,425 --> 00:17:04,625
If you're careless,

216
00:17:05,385 --> 00:17:07,625
she'll bite through your neck.

217
00:17:07,704 --> 00:17:10,184
What's bad about a biting wolf?

218
00:17:12,305 --> 00:17:15,944
Isn't that funnier than a dog
wagging its tail?

219
00:17:17,865 --> 00:17:19,545
Yanlai, you know that.

220
00:17:20,145 --> 00:17:21,704
I always like clever people.

221
00:17:29,065 --> 00:17:30,425
I've made my point.

222
00:17:31,425 --> 00:17:34,785
Young Master Xie,
be careful not to get burned.

223
00:17:50,905 --> 00:17:52,465
Thank you for your concern.

224
00:17:53,265 --> 00:17:54,585
When you have time,

225
00:17:55,705 --> 00:17:57,305
come back home.

226
00:17:58,265 --> 00:17:59,305
After all,

227
00:18:00,945 --> 00:18:02,145
you're a Xie.

228
00:18:15,705 --> 00:18:18,025
XIE

229
00:18:18,105 --> 00:18:21,945
XIE YANLAI, THE IMPERIAL GUARD COMMANDER

230
00:18:25,345 --> 00:18:26,425
Now you know

231
00:18:27,185 --> 00:18:29,585
why the Imperial Guard Tally
can't be given to Fu Jiu.

232
00:18:30,185 --> 00:18:33,545
He's a Xie. He's the ninth child
of the Xie Family,

233
00:18:34,545 --> 00:18:35,665
Xie Yanlai.

234
00:18:37,345 --> 00:18:38,465
I know.

235
00:18:40,105 --> 00:18:41,145
You know?

236
00:18:44,065 --> 00:18:46,745
He worked for my father for five years
under a false name.

237
00:18:46,825 --> 00:18:48,465
How could he not be exposed?

238
00:18:49,185 --> 00:18:52,145
You think my father's troops
didn't know his identity?

239
00:18:52,905 --> 00:18:55,625
They did. They just didn't care.

240
00:18:56,785 --> 00:18:59,025
Whether he's Fu Jiu or Xie Yanlai,

241
00:18:59,625 --> 00:19:03,225
if he had ill intentions
or harmed frontier troops,

242
00:19:03,305 --> 00:19:05,225
my father would punish him accordingly.

243
00:19:06,865 --> 00:19:09,465
But you gave the Tally
to someone from the Xie Clan.

244
00:19:10,065 --> 00:19:11,985
Do you know what that means?

245
00:19:16,225 --> 00:19:17,665
Calm down, Grand Mentor.

246
00:19:20,665 --> 00:19:23,425
I can give you more.

247
00:19:30,785 --> 00:19:34,945
Seven shops in Yongfeng Alley
will be put under your name tomorrow.

248
00:19:35,025 --> 00:19:38,385
Glazed cups and glowing pearls
aren't rare.

249
00:19:39,105 --> 00:19:40,585
Two boxes have been sent to you.

250
00:19:40,665 --> 00:19:42,345
Feel free to enjoy them.

251
00:19:43,385 --> 00:19:46,665
If you need anything else,
don't hesitate to tell me.

252
00:19:47,345 --> 00:19:50,505
I'll do my best to get it for you.

253
00:19:53,385 --> 00:19:54,705
Why, Your Highness?

254
00:19:56,385 --> 00:20:00,265
Do you know why the palace walls
can stand for a century?

255
00:20:00,945 --> 00:20:05,465
Because every brick
stays where it belongs.

256
00:20:06,065 --> 00:20:08,465
I made Xie Yanlai
the Imperial Guard Commander.

257
00:20:08,545 --> 00:20:11,265
But I'll count on you for court affairs.

258
00:20:12,505 --> 00:20:14,225
So rest assured, Mr. Deng.

259
00:20:14,785 --> 00:20:16,305
Before I'm no longer the princess,

260
00:20:16,905 --> 00:20:20,145
your position will be rock-solid.

261
00:20:24,145 --> 00:20:25,585
I will

262
00:20:26,585 --> 00:20:28,305
spare no effort.

263
00:20:31,985 --> 00:20:33,225
I've heard your mother

264
00:20:34,225 --> 00:20:36,065
has been missing the hometown.

265
00:20:36,145 --> 00:20:40,105
So I sent men at full gallop
to bring some millet from your hometown.

266
00:20:41,265 --> 00:20:42,305
It's nothing.

267
00:20:43,065 --> 00:20:45,345
Hearing you're a very good son,

268
00:20:45,425 --> 00:20:46,945
I'm just offering a little present.

269
00:20:49,225 --> 00:20:52,585
I… Thank you for your consideration.

270
00:20:54,665 --> 00:20:56,865
Everyone has his weakness.

271
00:20:57,585 --> 00:20:59,625
So do you, Deng Yi.

272
00:21:10,345 --> 00:21:12,545
Xie Yanfang is famous
throughout the state.

273
00:21:13,345 --> 00:21:15,705
But he still can't resist flattery.

274
00:21:16,225 --> 00:21:18,225
Since he likes obedient people,

275
00:21:19,305 --> 00:21:22,025
I'll sheathe my claws before him.

276
00:21:23,025 --> 00:21:23,945
As for Deng Yi…

277
00:21:25,905 --> 00:21:28,425
He's greedy and filial to his mother.

278
00:21:29,665 --> 00:21:31,025
I'll just give him what he wants.

279
00:21:36,705 --> 00:21:38,425
Xie Yanlai.

280
00:21:50,505 --> 00:21:52,625
All the ministers are fierce.

281
00:21:53,505 --> 00:21:54,785
He's the only one…

282
00:21:55,945 --> 00:21:57,985
who protects me with his own life.

283
00:22:02,905 --> 00:22:03,905
XIE YANLAI

284
00:22:03,985 --> 00:22:05,145
Jiu.

285
00:22:05,785 --> 00:22:07,345
I can trust you…

286
00:22:08,625 --> 00:22:09,465
right?

287
00:22:33,345 --> 00:22:34,185
Beat him!

288
00:22:34,265 --> 00:22:35,705
How dare you, an illegitimate son,

289
00:22:35,785 --> 00:22:38,185
burn the ancestors' tablets?

290
00:22:38,265 --> 00:22:40,985
You even angered your father to death.

291
00:22:41,065 --> 00:22:42,025
Believe it or not,

292
00:22:42,105 --> 00:22:44,465
I'll dig your mother out
and feed her to the dogs.

293
00:22:44,545 --> 00:22:46,225
Lowborn! You bring bad luck.

294
00:22:46,305 --> 00:22:47,465
Pah!

295
00:22:47,545 --> 00:22:49,065
Lowborn! Kill him!

296
00:22:49,145 --> 00:22:50,505
Hit him hard!

297
00:22:51,305 --> 00:22:52,865
Beat him to death!

298
00:22:53,465 --> 00:22:55,225
What is he doing?

299
00:22:57,945 --> 00:22:59,665
Are you killing Yanlai, Great-uncle?

300
00:23:00,265 --> 00:23:01,425
Father has just died.

301
00:23:01,505 --> 00:23:03,345
Do you want to lose another family member?

302
00:23:03,945 --> 00:23:06,465
But he burned the ancestral hall.

303
00:23:06,545 --> 00:23:08,585
-Right!
-Without descendants,

304
00:23:08,665 --> 00:23:09,905
what do we need the hall for?

305
00:23:10,825 --> 00:23:12,265
By killing a Xie descendant,

306
00:23:12,345 --> 00:23:13,945
will you answer to our ancestors?

307
00:23:14,025 --> 00:23:16,385
‎HONOR THE CLAN, UNITE THE KIN

308
00:23:23,545 --> 00:23:24,385
Yanlai.

309
00:23:29,665 --> 00:23:30,505
Yanlai.

310
00:23:33,225 --> 00:23:35,025
In childhood, you were afraid of pain.

311
00:23:35,985 --> 00:23:39,705
You cried in the barn
for an hour over your scraped knee.

312
00:23:40,945 --> 00:23:43,825
But today, you endured 18 lashes.
Like a different person.

313
00:23:46,745 --> 00:23:47,945
I'm Fu Jiu.

314
00:23:49,145 --> 00:23:49,985
I'm not your brother.

315
00:24:01,625 --> 00:24:03,145
I remember, when you were ten,

316
00:24:06,665 --> 00:24:08,545
you stole my books to pad the manger.

317
00:24:10,545 --> 00:24:12,065
I chased to the west yard

318
00:24:12,745 --> 00:24:17,025
and saw you wrapping
a crippled dog in the doghouse.

319
00:24:17,105 --> 00:24:19,785
At that time, you said
everything had a soul.

320
00:24:21,065 --> 00:24:22,545
A crippled dog shouldn't be discarded.

321
00:24:24,025 --> 00:24:25,705
But now, what's going on?

322
00:24:25,785 --> 00:24:27,105
When you're discarded,

323
00:24:27,985 --> 00:24:29,945
why do you let their words get to you?

324
00:24:30,025 --> 00:24:31,665
You're just like them!

325
00:24:32,865 --> 00:24:34,665
You look down on my mother and me.

326
00:24:35,265 --> 00:24:37,865
Why are you pretending
to be a caring brother?

327
00:24:48,745 --> 00:24:51,065
I am your elder brother.

328
00:24:52,345 --> 00:24:53,705
I don't need to pretend.

329
00:24:59,025 --> 00:25:01,065
‎XIE

330
00:25:28,825 --> 00:25:31,705
Jiu, you haven't fully recovered.
Why are you on night duty?

331
00:25:34,025 --> 00:25:36,865
It's not appropriate for you
to come so late.

332
00:25:39,905 --> 00:25:42,505
I'm just here to give you a cloak.

333
00:25:42,585 --> 00:25:44,985
You won't reject it, will you?

334
00:25:48,745 --> 00:25:50,185
I'm used to cotton.

335
00:25:50,705 --> 00:25:52,105
I won't like

336
00:25:52,825 --> 00:25:53,945
fancy fabrics.

337
00:26:02,105 --> 00:26:05,345
Cotton is too soft
to guard against arrows.

338
00:26:07,585 --> 00:26:08,745
Don't you agree?

339
00:26:10,745 --> 00:26:11,785
Mr. Xie Yanlai.

340
00:26:27,665 --> 00:26:29,625
Your Highness, are you testing me

341
00:26:32,225 --> 00:26:33,185
or trying to win me over?

342
00:26:33,825 --> 00:26:38,065
I heard when you served under my father,

343
00:26:38,145 --> 00:26:40,425
you didn't bat an eye
when breaking through ranks

344
00:26:40,505 --> 00:26:42,065
and pulled down the flag.

345
00:26:43,105 --> 00:26:44,625
But now,

346
00:26:45,305 --> 00:26:47,425
why are you afraid of a cloak?

347
00:26:48,785 --> 00:26:49,785
Afraid?

348
00:26:51,785 --> 00:26:53,825
Now I have the Imperial Guard Tally.

349
00:26:55,505 --> 00:26:56,625
Shouldn't you

350
00:26:59,305 --> 00:27:00,905
be the one who is afraid?

351
00:27:04,665 --> 00:27:06,145
I am afraid.

352
00:27:06,225 --> 00:27:07,985
Covert schemes are harder to dodge

353
00:27:08,585 --> 00:27:10,785
than open attacks on the frontier.

354
00:27:11,665 --> 00:27:14,265
So, Mr. Xie, will you consider

355
00:27:18,785 --> 00:27:20,265
becoming my ally?

356
00:28:08,385 --> 00:28:10,305
Now, you know who I am.

357
00:28:11,225 --> 00:28:13,345
Why do you think I'll pick your side

358
00:28:15,065 --> 00:28:16,145
instead of my own clan?

359
00:28:29,705 --> 00:28:31,425
Because I'll prove to you

360
00:28:32,025 --> 00:28:35,025
I'm more worthy of your support
than Xie Yanfang.

361
00:28:35,705 --> 00:28:38,185
Is this a deal or an order?

362
00:28:49,945 --> 00:28:51,545
It is a request.

363
00:29:05,745 --> 00:29:06,665
Your Highness,

364
00:29:07,785 --> 00:29:08,825
you're powerful now.

365
00:29:09,465 --> 00:29:11,425
Your request is too much for me.

366
00:29:12,745 --> 00:29:14,785
Let alone the support thing.

367
00:29:18,065 --> 00:29:19,305
You'd better

368
00:29:22,865 --> 00:29:24,185
take the cloak back.

369
00:29:42,145 --> 00:29:45,465
Life is like a chess game.
Nothing is set yet.

370
00:29:46,225 --> 00:29:49,665
Jiu, it's a little rash of you
to reject me so firmly.

371
00:29:57,665 --> 00:30:01,225
If one day, you change your mind,

372
00:30:01,905 --> 00:30:04,705
come to me anytime.

373
00:30:32,825 --> 00:30:33,825
Congratulations.

374
00:30:34,345 --> 00:30:38,985
You've become the Grand Princess
and gained the supreme power.

375
00:30:39,065 --> 00:30:41,705
You can finally take revenge.

376
00:30:41,785 --> 00:30:42,945
No.

377
00:30:45,505 --> 00:30:46,985
I want more than that.

378
00:30:47,705 --> 00:30:49,825
Don't you remember
how Xiao Xun strangled you,

379
00:30:49,905 --> 00:30:51,585
how he cut off your father's head,

380
00:30:51,665 --> 00:30:53,705
and how he annihilated your clan?

381
00:30:53,785 --> 00:30:55,025
Even if you have to lose your life,

382
00:30:55,105 --> 00:30:59,105
you should make Xiao Xun
pay blood for blood!

383
00:30:59,185 --> 00:31:02,785
Nothing but hatred
can get you up to the peak of power.

384
00:31:02,865 --> 00:31:06,385
Nothing but hatred
can make you use everyone,

385
00:31:06,465 --> 00:31:07,585
especially men.

386
00:31:07,665 --> 00:31:10,825
They're greedy for power
and beautiful women.

387
00:31:11,745 --> 00:31:13,425
If you don't mind,

388
00:31:13,505 --> 00:31:15,825
they will do anything for you.

389
00:31:16,505 --> 00:31:20,665
By then, you'll be able
to take revenge without bloodshed.

390
00:31:22,505 --> 00:31:23,625
Revenge.

391
00:31:26,705 --> 00:31:28,105
That's not my only desire.

392
00:31:28,185 --> 00:31:30,065
I do hate Xiao Xun.

393
00:31:30,145 --> 00:31:32,425
I also want to cut off his path to success

394
00:31:32,505 --> 00:31:35,065
and ruin everything he longs for.

395
00:31:36,145 --> 00:31:38,185
To make all this happen,

396
00:31:38,905 --> 00:31:40,385
I have to hide my abilities

397
00:31:41,145 --> 00:31:43,545
and conceal my edge for further action.

398
00:31:43,625 --> 00:31:45,785
With everything you have now?

399
00:31:46,385 --> 00:31:48,825
You're a princess in name only.

400
00:31:49,425 --> 00:31:50,745
Xiao Xun is the imperial uncle.

401
00:31:51,345 --> 00:31:52,825
Deng Yi oversees the court.

402
00:31:52,905 --> 00:31:54,585
The Xie Clan has accumulated merit.

403
00:31:54,665 --> 00:31:55,585
What do you have?

404
00:31:55,665 --> 00:31:57,265
What makes you think you can fight them?

405
00:31:58,105 --> 00:32:00,625
Didn't you risk your life
to become the Grand Princess

406
00:32:00,705 --> 00:32:03,105
just because you wanted Xiao Xun
to regret it

407
00:32:03,185 --> 00:32:07,705
and wanted to slice him
by the blade of power?

408
00:32:12,745 --> 00:32:13,585
No.

409
00:32:14,825 --> 00:32:16,345
I want more than this.

410
00:32:19,185 --> 00:32:20,545
I want to rule behind the curtain.

411
00:32:21,865 --> 00:32:23,585
I want the real power.

412
00:32:25,065 --> 00:32:26,505
I'll make my father and me

413
00:32:28,105 --> 00:32:30,105
live a long life.

414
00:32:34,065 --> 00:32:35,905
What I want is…

415
00:32:37,065 --> 00:32:39,905
Fate won't repeat itself.

416
00:32:56,065 --> 00:32:57,305
What?

417
00:32:57,385 --> 00:32:58,465
Yeah.

418
00:32:58,545 --> 00:33:00,025
The Grand Princess is here.

419
00:33:00,105 --> 00:33:01,385
That's utterly improper.

420
00:33:01,465 --> 00:33:03,305
It has never happened before.

421
00:33:03,385 --> 00:33:04,425
Indeed.

422
00:33:06,905 --> 00:33:08,345
Your Highness, it was all right

423
00:33:08,425 --> 00:33:11,705
that you attended
the enthronement ceremony.

424
00:33:12,305 --> 00:33:15,665
But now, how can you even attend court?

425
00:33:16,905 --> 00:33:19,785
Are you trying to rule behind the curtain

426
00:33:20,465 --> 00:33:22,265
just like Dowager Empress Xie?

427
00:33:22,345 --> 00:33:23,585
That's right.

428
00:33:23,665 --> 00:33:24,585
This is ridiculous.

429
00:33:24,665 --> 00:33:25,865
Outrageous, indeed.

430
00:33:27,105 --> 00:33:28,705
Who does she think she is?

431
00:33:28,785 --> 00:33:29,745
Come on.

432
00:33:30,345 --> 00:33:33,545
Ministers, my duty
is to oversee the court.

433
00:33:33,625 --> 00:33:35,585
His Majesty will rule sooner or later.

434
00:33:35,665 --> 00:33:37,865
His Majesty should attend court.

435
00:33:37,945 --> 00:33:40,345
Who made the rule
that Your Highness can attend court?

436
00:33:40,425 --> 00:33:42,465
Good question, Mr. Qin.

437
00:33:42,545 --> 00:33:44,065
A few days ago, you failed your duty.

438
00:33:44,665 --> 00:33:47,065
By law, you should have been executed.

439
00:33:47,145 --> 00:33:50,065
On the pretext of your military merit,
you were given a minor penalty.

440
00:33:50,145 --> 00:33:53,305
I also want to ask you.
Who made that rule?

441
00:33:55,105 --> 00:33:57,785
We've been sparing no effort
for our state.

442
00:33:57,865 --> 00:33:59,785
But now, in the court,

443
00:33:59,865 --> 00:34:01,425
a woman outside the royal clan

444
00:34:01,505 --> 00:34:04,345
takes charge of politics.
Isn't that ridiculous?

445
00:34:04,425 --> 00:34:05,865
Yeah. That's outrageous.

446
00:34:05,945 --> 00:34:07,305
That's right. That's absurd.

447
00:34:07,385 --> 00:34:08,865
Chamberlain,

448
00:34:08,945 --> 00:34:11,264
you're the father-in-law
of the Third Prince

449
00:34:11,344 --> 00:34:14,225
who killed his elder brother.

450
00:34:14,304 --> 00:34:15,865
If His Majesty hadn't shown mercy,

451
00:34:15,945 --> 00:34:19,065
you wouldn't be standing here and ranting.

452
00:34:19,665 --> 00:34:23,225
Instead of feeling grateful,
you make things difficult.

453
00:34:23,304 --> 00:34:25,945
Aren't you biting the hand that feeds you?

454
00:34:26,025 --> 00:34:28,505
It's perceptive of you, Mr. Deng.

455
00:34:29,344 --> 00:34:32,625
You've figured out everything
about all the ministers.

456
00:34:32,705 --> 00:34:34,465
How admirable.

457
00:34:35,025 --> 00:34:38,065
Within only a few days,
you've put in so much effort.

458
00:34:39,025 --> 00:34:41,065
This is truly a blessing for this state.

459
00:34:41,824 --> 00:34:43,705
When you assist His Majesty so well,

460
00:34:43,784 --> 00:34:46,505
our state will be peaceful.

461
00:34:46,585 --> 00:34:48,505
Entrusted by the late Emperor,

462
00:34:48,585 --> 00:34:50,625
I dare not slack off in my duty.

463
00:34:50,705 --> 00:34:54,225
Mr. Xie, you used to be sick
and away from court for years.

464
00:34:54,304 --> 00:34:56,344
When you're back here,

465
00:34:56,425 --> 00:34:58,425
you must have a lot of confusions.

466
00:34:59,265 --> 00:35:01,905
If you want to discuss anything with me,

467
00:35:01,985 --> 00:35:03,865
I'm always at your service.

468
00:35:05,225 --> 00:35:07,345
Ministers, present your reports,

469
00:35:07,425 --> 00:35:08,945
or the court is dismissed.

470
00:35:10,185 --> 00:35:11,625
But… This…

471
00:35:12,945 --> 00:35:14,025
How could she say that?

472
00:35:14,785 --> 00:35:17,025
What a breach of rules.

473
00:35:19,265 --> 00:35:20,425
Who does she think she is?

474
00:35:20,505 --> 00:35:22,625
She has no right to say that.

475
00:35:22,705 --> 00:35:23,945
She oversteps her authority.

476
00:35:24,025 --> 00:35:26,185
She… She's being presumptuous.

477
00:35:27,025 --> 00:35:28,665
-Yeah.
-Who would accept that?

478
00:35:28,745 --> 00:35:29,785
Yeah.

479
00:35:30,385 --> 00:35:31,425
Commander Xie.

480
00:35:35,145 --> 00:35:36,105
Her Highness ordered!

481
00:35:37,025 --> 00:35:38,265
Present your reports!

482
00:35:38,825 --> 00:35:40,065
Or the court is dismissed!

483
00:35:49,265 --> 00:35:52,105
I… I have something to report.

484
00:35:53,225 --> 00:35:57,025
Recently, I dreamed
that the late Emperor wept blood,

485
00:35:57,545 --> 00:35:58,745
yearning for temple rites.

486
00:36:00,185 --> 00:36:02,785
The late Emperor should
cry out to the current emperor.

487
00:36:02,865 --> 00:36:06,065
Why would a hostage like you
say such things?

488
00:36:06,945 --> 00:36:09,145
In that case, Mr. Xiao must have

489
00:36:09,225 --> 00:36:12,905
a close connection with the late Emperor
because they're blood-related.

490
00:36:12,985 --> 00:36:14,865
But oddly enough…

491
00:36:15,425 --> 00:36:16,505
Mr. Xiao,

492
00:36:16,585 --> 00:36:19,625
why didn't you dream of the Crown Prince?

493
00:36:19,705 --> 00:36:21,505
Does the late Emperor also think

494
00:36:21,585 --> 00:36:25,385
your branch is closer to him
than the Crown Prince?

495
00:36:26,705 --> 00:36:30,065
So, last night, Grandfather
appeared in Uncle's dream.

496
00:36:30,145 --> 00:36:31,945
He must have been angry with me.

497
00:36:32,745 --> 00:36:35,145
In the past few days,
he often came into my dreams,

498
00:36:35,225 --> 00:36:37,065
saying he would fly a kite with me.

499
00:36:37,145 --> 00:36:38,465
But last night, he didn't appear.

500
00:36:38,545 --> 00:36:39,585
Yu.

501
00:36:47,545 --> 00:36:51,745
Your Highness,
what do you think we should do?

502
00:36:59,265 --> 00:37:01,065
Since His Majesty had dreams,

503
00:37:01,745 --> 00:37:06,985
Mr. Deng and Mr. Xie
shall prepare for the sacrifice thing.

504
00:37:07,065 --> 00:37:10,625
We'll do our best.

505
00:37:25,185 --> 00:37:27,065
It's so tiring to attend court.

506
00:37:27,145 --> 00:37:28,625
Can I not go tomorrow?

507
00:37:30,105 --> 00:37:34,305
Yu, an emperor must put the state first
instead of complaining all the time.

508
00:37:36,985 --> 00:37:39,545
-Where's my Nine-ring Puzzle?
-Back there.

509
00:37:40,985 --> 00:37:42,785
Watch your step. Don't trip.

510
00:37:42,865 --> 00:37:43,705
All right.

511
00:37:48,985 --> 00:37:51,745
Without requesting an audience,
I came in here uninvited.

512
00:37:52,265 --> 00:37:54,425
Please forgive me, Your Highness.

513
00:37:57,665 --> 00:37:59,825
You're Yu's close family.

514
00:37:59,905 --> 00:38:01,705
And now I'm his sister.

515
00:38:02,305 --> 00:38:03,745
You and I are close too.

516
00:38:04,905 --> 00:38:08,265
You don't need to inform others
before you visit Yu.

517
00:38:09,065 --> 00:38:12,025
But now, he's the Emperor, after all.

518
00:38:12,105 --> 00:38:15,785
I hope you'll inform me next time,

519
00:38:16,345 --> 00:38:18,705
so that I can be prepared.

520
00:38:20,865 --> 00:38:21,825
I'll keep that in mind.

521
00:38:26,145 --> 00:38:27,225
Yu.

522
00:38:32,185 --> 00:38:33,705
-I'm your…
-Uncle.

523
00:38:34,385 --> 00:38:35,505
Be careful.

524
00:38:42,785 --> 00:38:45,065
You brought a toy to
today's court, didn't you?

525
00:38:45,145 --> 00:38:47,385
It's just a Nine-ring Puzzle.

526
00:38:51,785 --> 00:38:52,745
Give it to me.

527
00:38:54,385 --> 00:38:55,985
I know I was wrong.

528
00:39:01,065 --> 00:39:02,385
Never do it again.

529
00:39:10,225 --> 00:39:11,385
Yu,

530
00:39:11,905 --> 00:39:14,265
this is Mr. Xie Yanfang from the Xie Clan.

531
00:39:15,065 --> 00:39:16,465
He's also your uncle.

532
00:39:19,585 --> 00:39:20,985
Xie Yanfang?

533
00:39:23,065 --> 00:39:24,105
Oh, the Third Uncle.

534
00:39:35,705 --> 00:39:36,625
Yu,

535
00:39:38,745 --> 00:39:41,785
I know you hate my clan and me.

536
00:39:42,385 --> 00:39:45,625
We failed to protect your parents
as well as you.

537
00:39:46,265 --> 00:39:49,465
So, I came here today to apologize to you.

538
00:39:51,665 --> 00:39:54,185
From now on, I'll spare no effort

539
00:39:55,265 --> 00:39:56,465
to keep you safe.

540
00:39:58,305 --> 00:40:01,105
Yu, it's time for morning classes.

541
00:40:01,185 --> 00:40:03,505
Go wait for me in the study, will you?

542
00:40:13,145 --> 00:40:14,305
He's a kid,

543
00:40:14,905 --> 00:40:18,785
and it's normal that he doesn't know
how to hide his emotions.

544
00:40:24,265 --> 00:40:26,065
Don't bother to console me.

545
00:40:26,705 --> 00:40:30,505
We do feel sorry for the massacre
of the Crown Prince's family.

546
00:40:32,025 --> 00:40:34,065
We arrived too late to protect them.

547
00:40:35,705 --> 00:40:37,145
Yu harbors some resentment,

548
00:40:38,625 --> 00:40:39,985
and I understand.

549
00:40:41,145 --> 00:40:42,825
Yu is still young.

550
00:40:42,905 --> 00:40:46,625
After such a tragedy,
his temperament changed somewhat.

551
00:40:47,145 --> 00:40:48,625
Later on, he'll get better.

552
00:40:49,985 --> 00:40:51,225
Next time you come,

553
00:40:51,905 --> 00:40:55,225
bring him some toys,
and that might cheer him up.

554
00:41:02,265 --> 00:41:03,225
How rare.

555
00:41:04,865 --> 00:41:08,665
The two of you match well in character.

556
00:41:15,105 --> 00:41:16,625
How enviable.

557
00:41:18,425 --> 00:41:19,265
Yeah.

558
00:41:20,305 --> 00:41:21,585
Commander Xie is exceptionally brave.

559
00:41:22,705 --> 00:41:24,065
I admire him a lot.

560
00:41:24,665 --> 00:41:27,705
I'll count on him
for the safety of the imperial palace.

561
00:41:46,505 --> 00:41:48,585
You know Xie Yanfang is suspicious.

562
00:41:49,305 --> 00:41:52,145
But in front of him,
you pretended to think highly of me.

563
00:41:52,865 --> 00:41:53,705
What were you up to?

564
00:41:53,785 --> 00:41:55,745
You didn't deny it just now.

565
00:41:56,345 --> 00:41:58,945
So, you agreed
that I was telling the truth.

566
00:42:00,545 --> 00:42:02,305
Does it mean

567
00:42:04,465 --> 00:42:06,065
you've accepted my offer?

568
00:42:13,425 --> 00:42:15,305
It's my duty to protect Your Highness.

569
00:42:16,265 --> 00:42:17,305
Not because of your offer.

570
00:42:17,905 --> 00:42:19,225
Then have you decided?

571
00:42:20,465 --> 00:42:22,385
Once you're the Commander,

572
00:42:23,585 --> 00:42:25,505
you won't go back to Yunzhong.

573
00:42:27,145 --> 00:42:28,385
I was a retainer of your family.

574
00:42:30,345 --> 00:42:31,545
I don't care about that.

575
00:42:32,225 --> 00:42:34,625
As for you, the Grand Princess,

576
00:42:35,825 --> 00:42:37,265
there's really no turning back.

577
00:42:45,625 --> 00:42:46,825
Is this

578
00:42:48,585 --> 00:42:49,785
what you really want?

579
00:42:52,705 --> 00:42:54,985
Xie Yanfang is the head of ministers.

580
00:42:55,065 --> 00:42:56,145
Deng Yi controls speech.

581
00:42:56,825 --> 00:42:59,145
Xiao Xun owns Xiaonan Prefecture.

582
00:42:59,705 --> 00:43:00,785
But you…

583
00:43:02,025 --> 00:43:03,225
What do you have?

584
00:43:11,265 --> 00:43:13,785
I have you, who will risk his life for me.

585
00:43:27,425 --> 00:43:29,025
Two against two. I won't be scared.

586
00:43:29,625 --> 00:43:32,265
Even if Xiao Xun interferes,
we have Xiao Yu.

587
00:43:32,785 --> 00:43:34,345
Three against three, then.

588
00:43:35,345 --> 00:43:36,825
Besides,

589
00:43:38,465 --> 00:43:40,065
you can fight against not only two,

590
00:43:41,865 --> 00:43:44,065
but even a hundred more.

591
00:43:57,265 --> 00:43:59,985
I want you to handle Deng Yi
and Xie Yanfang.

592
00:44:00,065 --> 00:44:03,425
But Jiu, you look like
you want to devour me.

593
00:44:12,745 --> 00:44:13,825
You should figure out

594
00:44:14,545 --> 00:44:15,985
how to handle Xiao Xun first.

595
00:44:16,065 --> 00:44:18,225
He suddenly proposed the sacrifice.

596
00:44:19,025 --> 00:44:20,225
He must have a plan.

597
00:44:21,345 --> 00:44:22,545
I know.

598
00:44:22,625 --> 00:44:23,985
You know?

599
00:44:25,385 --> 00:44:27,345
Then how can you remain so calm?

600
00:44:27,945 --> 00:44:31,185
If I panicked, what would that change?

601
00:44:32,545 --> 00:44:34,505
I prefer to stay put and wait.

602
00:44:34,585 --> 00:44:39,025
I'll see how he's going to play his game.

603
00:47:08,825 --> 00:47:13,665
Subtitle translation by:
